.SH "HISTORY"
.IX Header "HISTORY"
The \fBlhash\fR library is available in all versions of SSLeay and OpenSSL.
\&\fIlh_error()\fR was added in SSLeay 0.9.1b.
.PP
This manpage is derived from the SSLeay documentation.
.PP
